{"tid":2488024,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［真三國］如果韓信自立， 同劉邦項羽三分天下會點","createTime":"2021-04-14T03:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T03:43:27.000Z","uid":23495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1427badb1303d70151496c20fc2ba64ce82ff5fa","tid":2488024,"uid":23495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:16:14.000Z","msg":"假設韓信知道自己功高蓋主<br />\n收風得知劉邦會係得天下後肅清自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n索性聽蒯通話自立做齊皇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韓信 項羽 劉邦天下三分<br />\n邊個會得天下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n項羽自傲 雖然打仗戰無不勝 <br />\n但戰略用人都差 應該都係會輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該都係世界仔劉邦同韓信之爭"},{"pid":"34866f6fcbe485805b8a70c1058ac89594be518a","tid":2488024,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:20:21.000Z","msg":"GG"},{"pid":"120b5aa004db086f217849d6d8959d1180560fdf","tid":2488024,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:21:10.000Z","msg":"理論上打仗韓信無敵"},{"pid":"e5352d29c9375502d99a4ba7fdc321928c3e7e5a","tid":2488024,"uid":245201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:22:06.000Z","msg":"將呢？兵呢？有冇豪強支持？<br />\n手下有咩叻人幫佢度橋？果個叻人係樓主你？"},{"pid":"eaec87c32b3caa80ff747fd23c40ae97e780cecf","tid":2488024,"uid":206522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:23:52.000Z","msg":"咁中國人會變成韓國人"},{"pid":"e78cb0bdfd0f32953a2e0a7b43de8d03a3684b8a","tid":2488024,"uid":23495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"120b5aa004db086f217849d6d8959d1180560fdf","tid":2488024,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:21:10.000Z","msg":"理論上打仗韓信無敵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:31:47.000Z","msg":"韓信項羽打仗係勁  <br />\n但正史都係死係劉邦手上<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再者韓信其實同項羽未正面對決過<br />\n唯一 一次垓下天下圍攻